Fish Fillets NG - 0.5.0
* removed libboost dependence
* options menu on F10
* 19 new levels
* credits
* initial German translation
* some new options, see man page


Fish Fillets NG - 0.4.1
* fixed level wreck crash
* fixed pyramid animation, level music music ;)
